    <p><b><span id="Overview">Objective:</span></b> <span id="md-webpage-description" itemprop="description">The objective of <i>ITIL Risk Management</i> is to identify, assess and control risks. This includes analyzing the value of assets to the business, identifying threats to those assets, and evaluating how vulnerable each asset is to those threats.</span></p>
    <p><b>Part of</b>: Service Design </p>
    <p><b>Process Owner</b>: Risk Manager </p>
    <p>&#160;</p>
